name: TEN
public_notice:
TENFI is undergoing a contract migration from V1 TENFI to V2 TENFI.
For more information please refer to: https://medium.com/tenfinance/ten-x-new-tenfi-8d21000c3b95
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: TEN simplifies staking and farming with the most liquid BSC LP's available and provides a robust yield earning environment on the market while adapting to daily liquidity needs of different pools. TEN is decentralized finance, simplified!
